Provides: niri
Description: Scrollable-tiling Wayland compositor (git development version)
 niri is a scrollable-tiling Wayland compositor built from the git master
 branch. It provides a unique scrollable tiling layout that allows for
 infinite workspace scrolling.
 .
 Features include:
  - Scrollable tiling layout
  - Smooth animations
  - Dynamic workspaces
  - Built-in screen recording support
  - Full Wayland protocol support
  - Systemd integration
  - XDG desktop portal support
 .
 This is the development version built from git master with the latest
 features. For a stable release, use the 'niri' package instead.
